          "AdditionalTradeItemDescription": [
            {
              "LanguageCode": "en",
              "Value": "Erland Care Protective Skin 7,5 x 7,5 cm.\n\nProtective Skin is a skin-friendly, waterproof and superabsorbent silicone dressing that allows the skin to breathe. It can absorb mild to moderate exuding wounds. The dressing is suitable for users with fragile/sensitive skin and for those who are vulnerable to skin damage. As the product is thin, soft and very flexible it conforms to the contours of the body. It is suitable for applying to challenging areas such as joints. Protective Skin is easy to apply and remove without stripping the skin. It can be removed and re applied up to 10 times without losing its adhesion."
